        Create a new filter range with the given parameters. A null start indicates an open ended start, while a null end indicates an open ended end.
        Parameters:
        start - the start of the range
        end - the end of the range
        startInclusive - whether or not the start is inclusive
        endInclusive - whether or not the end is inclusive
        exact - whether or not this range exactly represents the predicate
